      "body" : "One thing to keep in mind though with <code>Collections.emptyList()</code>, the list is immutable, you can add any items to it. If you are just reading from the list, then this is fine, but if you want to add items you will need a new list object. IIRC if you do try to add to a <code>Collections.emptyList()</code>, the error message isn&#39;t the most helpful."
