      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@RobertoLinares that&#39;s technically fine but if you have no plans to add items to the list it&#39;s more efficient to use one of the options from Collections. Going back to the original question, the intention here is to avoid hitting a NullPointerException so making a brand new List wouldn&#39;t benefit you."
