      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Another similar approach using Java&#39;s native <code>Objects</code> class is<code>Objects.requireNonNullElse(itemsList, new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;())</code>"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
