    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 45,
    "last_activity_date" : 1495076602,
    "creation_date" : 1495076602,
    "answer_id" : 44037919,
    "question_id" : 2250031,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It's already 2017, and you can now use <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-collections/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Apache Commons Collections4</a></p>\n\n<p>The usage:<br>\n</p>\n\n<pre><code>for(Object obj : ListUtils.emptyIfNull(list1)){\n    // Do your stuff\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can do the same null-safe check to other Collection classes with <code>CollectionUtils.emptyIfNull</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
