    "question_id" : 2250031,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>With Java 8 <code>Optional</code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>for (Object object : Optional.ofNullable(someList).orElse(Collections.emptyList())) {\n    // do whatever\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7874694,
      "reputation" : 1682,
      "user_id" : 5950846,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 50,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/n6Op0.jpg?s=256",
